<ul><li> <em>When They're Gone</em> (<a class="urllink" href="http://www.fanfiction.net/s/4112580/1/When_Theyre_Gone">seen here<img src="https://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/external_link.gif" height="12" width="12" style="border:none;"></a>) features Shinji cross-dressing as a major plot point. He proves to be so attractive when doing this that many of his straight schoolmates begin questioning their sexualities.
